    "info": {
        "name": "AiHospitality API v1",
        "description": "Complete API collection for AiHospitality hospitality management platform.\n\n## Authentication\nAll endpoints require Bearer token authentication.\n\n## Base URL\n```\nhttps://api.aihospitality.com/api/v1\n```\n\n## Headers\n- `Authorization`: Bearer {token}\n- `Content-Type`: application/json\n- `x-hotelid` OR `x-hubid`: Property context (mutually exclusive)\n- `x-request-id`: Optional request tracking ID",
